<br />
<br />The idea I have is that the shield will work for small bullets.  You get ONE shield hit and it is recharged at a nonagram.  Spikes or physically touching an enemy still = death.  Large bullets (i.e. stuff that's more than 8x8 pixels) will most likely be 1 hitters too.

		

